quotes.text: “Two things are infinite: the universe and human stupidity; and I'm not sure about the universe.”
quotes.author: Albert Einstein

quotes.text: “Don’t walk in front of me… I may not follow Don’t walk behind me… I may not lead Walk beside me… just be my friend”
quotes.author: Albert Camus

quotes.text: “If you tell the truth, you don't have to remember anything.”
quotes.author: Mark Twain

quotes.text: "Education is the most powerful weapon which you can use to change the world."
quotes.author: Nelson Mandela

quotes.text: "If you want to lift yourself up, lift up someone else."
quotes.author: Booker T. Washington

quotes.text: "I scorched the earth with my talent and I let my light shine."
quotes.author: André Leon Talley

quotes.text: "You’re braver than you believe, stronger than you seem, and smarter than you think."
quotes.author: A.A. Milne

quotes.text: “Experience is not what happens to you; it is what you do with what happens to you.”
quotes.author: Aldous Huxley
